; Tests for the quantity() function
; Extracts the numeric portion from an amount, stripping the commodity

2012-01-01 Test quantity function
    Assets:Test                       $100.00
    Equity:Opening

; Positive test: extract quantity from dollar amount
test eval 'quantity($100)'
100
end test

; Positive test: extract quantity from EUR amount
test eval 'quantity(50 EUR)'
